{"name": "odoo-addon-product-price-category", "metadata": {"name": "odoo-addon-product-price-category", "version": "16.0.1.0.0.6", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 16.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo"], "summary": "Add Price Category field on product and allow to apply a pricelist on this field.", "upload_time": 1729059541}, "documentation": ["```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.svg\n:alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n:target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl\n```\n\n# Product Price Category\n\nThis module adds a field Price Category on Product Template\nand allow Pricelist to be applied on this field.\n\n## Usage\n\nIn Pricelist Form (Sales -> Configuration -> Pricelist), you can add or modify\nan item (\"Manage Pricelist Items\" access should be checked in the user settings)\nand select \"Price Category\" in \"Applied on\".\nThen you have to choose on which price category should it be applied.\n\n```{image} static/pricelist_price_category.png\n```\n\nProduct price category can be modified in product form -> General Information.\n\n```{image} static/product_price_category.png\n```\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/website/image/ir.attachment/5784_f2813bd/datas\n:alt: Try me on Runbot\n:target: https://runbot.odoo-community.org/runbot/167/10.0\n```\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow/issues). In case of trouble, please\ncheck there if your issue has already been reported. If you spotted it first,\nhelp us smash it by providing detailed and welcomed feedback.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Images\n\n- Odoo Community Association: [Icon](https://github.com/OCA/maintainer-tools/blob/master/template/module/static/description/icon.svg).\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Cyril Gaudin \\<<mailto:cyril.gaudin@camptocamp.com>>\n- Akim Juillerat \\<<mailto:akim.juillerat@camptocamp.com>>\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n### Maintainer\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nTo contribute to this module, please visit <https://odoo-community.org>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_price_category.models.product_pricelist", "documentation": ["Copyright 2017 Camptocamp SA", "Copyright 2023 ACSONE SA/NV", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_price_category.models.product_pricelist.ProductPricelist", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_price_category.models.product_pricelist.ProductPricelist._get_applicable_rules_domain", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "products", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "date", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "**kwargs", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_price_category.models.product_pricelist.ProductPricelist._inherit", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_price_category.models.product_pricelist_item", "documentation": ["Copyright 2017 Camptocamp SA", "Copyright 2023 ACSONE SA/NV", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_price_category.models.product_pricelist_item.ProductPricelistItem", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_price_category.models.product_pricelist_item.ProductPricelistItem._compute_name_and_price", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_price_category.models.product_pricelist_item.ProductPricelistItem._compute_price_category", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Reset the price_category_id value if applied_on\nis not price_category"]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_price_category.models.product_pricelist_item.ProductPricelistItem._is_applicable_for", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "product", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "qty_in_product_uom", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_price_category.models.product_pricelist_item.ProductPricelistItem._inherit", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_price_category.models.product_pricelist_item.ProductPricelistItem.applied_on", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_price_category.models.product_pricelist_item.ProductPricelistItem.price_category_id", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_price_category.models.product_price_category", "documentation": ["Copyright 2016 Camptocamp SA", "Copyright 2023 ACSONE SA/NV", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_price_category.models.product_price_category.ProductPriceCategory", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_pr